sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Executor
    participant Middleware as Middleware Chain
    participant Registry
    participant Formatter as Formatter (native/service)
    participant Cache as InMemoryCache

    Client->>+Executor: Execute(ctx, FormatRequest)

    Note over Executor: Resolve formatter from<br/>Language or FilePath

    alt Language specified
        Executor->>+Registry: GetByLanguage(language)
        Registry-->>-Executor: []Formatter
    else FilePath specified
        Executor->>+Registry: DetectFormatter(filePath)
        Registry->>Registry: DetectLanguageFromPath(filePath)
        Registry->>Registry: GetByLanguage(detected)
        Registry-->>-Executor: Formatter
    end

    Note over Executor: Build middleware chain

    Executor->>+Middleware: executeFunc(ctx, formatter, req)

    Note over Middleware: ValidationMiddleware:<br/>Check non-empty input

    Middleware->>Middleware: TimeoutMiddleware: ctx with deadline

    Middleware->>Middleware: RetryMiddleware: attempt loop

    alt Cache enabled (application-level)
        Middleware->>+Cache: Get(req)
        Cache-->>-Middleware: (result, hit)
        alt Cache hit
            Middleware-->>Executor: cached FormatResult
        end
    end

    Middleware->>+Formatter: Format(ctx, req)

    alt NativeFormatter
        Formatter->>Formatter: buildArgs(req)
        Formatter->>Formatter: exec.CommandContext(binary, args)
        Formatter->>Formatter: pipe stdin, capture stdout/stderr
        Formatter->>Formatter: computeLineChanges()
    else ServiceFormatter
        Formatter->>Formatter: Marshal ServiceFormatRequest
        Formatter->>Formatter: POST endpoint/format
        Formatter->>Formatter: Unmarshal ServiceFormatResponse
    end

    Formatter-->>-Middleware: FormatResult

    Note over Middleware: ValidationMiddleware:<br/>Check non-empty output

    alt Cache enabled (application-level)
        Middleware->>Cache: Set(req, result)
    end

    Middleware-->>-Executor: FormatResult

    Note over Executor: Set result.Duration

    Executor-->>-Client: FormatResult
